{"id":1707,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":426,"title":"Conversation 216","subtitle":"Charity Event Flyer Printing","level":"B1","parts":16,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-216.1707/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/0-conversation-216.mp3","transcript":"Hello! Can I help you with something today?\nYes, please.\nI'm organizing a charity event and I need to print 200 flyers.\nI'm not sure which paper would be best\nsince I want them to stand out but also be affordable.\nAny suggestions?\nCertainly!\nI would recommend our matte finish paper.\nIt's cost-effective and the colors really pop,\nmaking it perfect for eye-catching flyers.\nThat sounds like a great option.\nCould you tell me how much the total cost will be?\nOf course!\nEach sheet with the matte finish is 25 cents,\nand we can print two flyers per sheet.\nSo your total will be $25.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:03:34","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hello! Can I help you with something today?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/1.mp3","time_start":0.0,"time_end":2.29},{"position":2,"content":"Yes, please.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/2.mp3","time_start":2.49,"time_end":3.53},{"position":3,"content":"I'm organizing a charity event and I need to print 200 flyers.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/3.mp3","time_start":3.53,"time_end":7.68},{"position":4,"content":"I'm not sure which paper would be best","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/4.mp3","time_start":7.87,"time_end":9.98},{"position":5,"content":"since I want them to stand out but also be affordable.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/5.mp3","time_start":9.98,"time_end":13.02},{"position":6,"content":"Any suggestions?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/6.mp3","time_start":13.02,"time_end":14.64},{"position":7,"content":"Certainly!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/7.mp3","time_start":15.02,"time_end":16.1},{"position":8,"content":"I would recommend our matte finish paper.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/8.mp3","time_start":16.1,"time_end":18.45},{"position":9,"content":"It's cost-effective and the colors really pop,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/9.mp3","time_start":18.45,"time_end":21.16},{"position":10,"content":"making it perfect for eye-catching flyers.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/10.mp3","time_start":21.16,"time_end":23.77},{"position":11,"content":"That sounds like a great option.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/11.mp3","time_start":24.09,"time_end":25.81},{"position":12,"content":"Could you tell me how much the total cost will be?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/12.mp3","time_start":25.81,"time_end":28.52},{"position":13,"content":"Of course!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/13.mp3","time_start":28.67,"time_end":29.66},{"position":14,"content":"Each sheet with the matte finish is 25 cents,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/14.mp3","time_start":29.66,"time_end":32.73},{"position":15,"content":"and we can print two flyers per sheet.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-216-2024-10-22-12-56-05/15.mp3","time_start":3